Today this palace has good assets.

This mosque is currently one of the mosques that offer Friday prayers.

There is a spacious place for namaz, including for women.
There is a good facility to listen to the khutbah.
It is so simple that listeners can easily understand it.
There is AC.

There is a necessary facility to park the vehicles of the visitors.

And for taking vulu.
Good facility.
There are also toilets.

The mosque and its surroundings are a very beautiful place.
Many people come here daily to pray.

Subahi Namaz is generally less crowded.
There is no restriction on resting or using a fan like in some mosques.
Be careful to reduce unnecessary usage.

Mosques are central places of Islamic worship. According to Islamic belief, mosques are places where Muslims pray.
Muslims go to pray in a regular mosque or mosque.

The mosque closes as soon as the Isha prayer is completed.
However, it is possible to make use of the small facility of praying outside
